--help
USAGE: 
	sudo ./cli [start] [stop] [show [ip] count] [select iface [iface]] stat[iface] 
	start - packets are being sniffed from now on from default iface (eth0) 
	stop - packets are not sniffed 
 	show [ip] count - print number of packets received from selected ip address 
 	select_iface [iface] - select interface for sniffing eth0, wlan0, ethN, wlanN 
	stat [iface] - show all collected statistics for particular interface, if iface ommited - for all interfaces

 
